      <div>
        <h2 id="whats-new">What’s New</h2>
        <p>Stay up-to-date with the latest releases and enhancements in the SAP Design System, and informed with insights from design experts.</p>
        <div class="cards">
          <div>
            <div>
              <picture>
                <source type="image/webp" srcset="./media_127b2e2a48cb289677995293e8876e55ab1689d4c.png?width=2000&#x26;format=webply&#x26;optimize=medium" media="(min-width: 600px)">
