            <div>align-image-left</div>
            <div>
              <h3 id="designing-the-autonomous-enterprise">Designing the Autonomous Enterprise</h3>
              <p>As announced at Sapphire, Joule Work is an entirely new way to engage with and execute end-to-end business processes with AI collaboration. Read more to learn how SAP’s AI experience is redefining work.</p>
              <p><a href="https://www.sap.com/design/stories-resources/designing-the-autonomous-enterprise">See the news</a></p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
