              <h3 id="sap-design-system-is-powering-ai-led-product-design">SAP Design System is powering AI-led product design</h3>
              <p>Product illustrations as more than decoration; they’re a tool to communicate clearly, quickly, and meaningfully with our users.</p>
              <p><a href="https://www.sap.com/design/stories-resources/sap-design-system-is-powering-the-next-generation-of-ai-led-prod">See the recap</a></p>
