            <div>align-image-left</div>
            <div>
              <p>Tailored. User experience.</p>
              <h3 id="optimized-for-many-form-factors">Optimized for many form factors</h3>
              <p>The SAP Design System is designed to provide a truly cross-platform experience. Across devices, working conditions, and locations, users get their best work done anywhere, any time.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
