              <p>Inclusive. User experience.</p>
              <h3 id="accessible-and-inclusive-from-the-start">Accessible and inclusive from the start</h3>
              <p>Making enterprise software as accessible and inclusive as possible is not a nice-to-have but rather a must-have. The SAP Design System is built on a foundation of inclusive and accessible design in order to best serve as many users as possible.</p>
